rows.label: qst201901_0010
rows.name: We've come to quite a remote place.

rows.label: qst201901_0020
rows.name: Rinne... what are we doing here?

rows.label: qst201901_0030
rows.name: ...Hmph. Are your eyes merely for show?

rows.label: qst201901_0040
rows.name:
Behold! This white sand beach
and this beautiful lake...

rows.label: qst201901_0050
rows.name:
A grand mansion by the lakeside,
perfect for a vacation...

rows.label: qst201901_0060
rows.name:
This is the tropical paradise that all the girls of the
world long for... a resort island to be envied by all.

rows.label: qst201901_0070
rows.name: ...But there's nothing here at all!

rows.label: qst201901_0080
rows.name: To acquire an island like this...

rows.label: qst201901_0090
rows.name: We paid... one million gold?!

rows.label: qst201901_0100
rows.name: One million...

rows.label: qst201901_0110
rows.name: Wait, Rinne? You bought this island?

rows.label: qst201901_0120
rows.name:
The one million gold that
we scrimped and saved...

rows.label: qst201901_0130
rows.name:
It was my dream to own a luxurious mansion on
a beautiful little island, and there... yes.

rows.label: qst201901_0140
rows.name:
With many lovely girls gathered
from all over the world...

rows.label: qst201901_0150
rows.name: ...to hold an elegant tea party...

rows.label: qst201901_0160
rows.name:
What am I supposed to do on this
empty, pitiful little island...?

rows.label: qst201901_0170
rows.name: ...Ye were scammed.

rows.label: qst201901_0180
rows.name: Definitely scammed, mo.

rows.label: qst201901_0190
rows.name: ...Ah, yes. We were scammed.

rows.label: qst201901_0200
rows.name:
...That Superbian black-feathered
fool swindled all our money.

rows.label: qst201901_0210
rows.name: Black-feathered fool?

rows.label: qst201901_0220
rows.name: Most likely a Nopon merchant.

rows.label: qst201901_0230
rows.name:
I see. So the culprit
has been identified.

rows.label: qst201901_0240
rows.name: Then this is simple.

rows.label: qst201901_0250
rows.name:
That's right... We just have to
get the money back from him.

rows.label: qst201901_0260
rows.name: Come on, cheer up.

rows.label: qst201901_0270
rows.name: ...Nia, Meleph, and Kagutsuchi...

rows.label: qst201901_0280
rows.name: Will you lend us your hand?

rows.label: qst201901_0290
rows.name: Of course.

rows.label: qst201901_0300
rows.name:
If we leave that merchant be,
there may be more victims.

rows.label: qst201901_0310
rows.name: We should deal with this promptly.

rows.label: qst201901_0320
rows.name: Oh... my beloved friends.

rows.label: qst201901_0330
rows.name:
You are the only ones who
truly worry for us...

rows.label: qst201901_0340
rows.name:
As a token of my gratitude, I shall prepare
a special seat for you in my harem.

rows.label: qst201901_0350
rows.name: ...No thanks.

rows.label: qst201901_0360
rows.name: Indeed... I may be unworthy.

rows.label: qst201901_0370
rows.name: Yes... Your gratitude alone is enough.

rows.label: qst201901_0380
rows.name: Is that so? How cold...

rows.label: qst201901_0390
rows.name:
Very well... More importantly,
that wretched fool.

rows.label: qst201901_0400
rows.name:
To approach us with that vacant face
and toy with our pure heart...

rows.label: qst201901_0410
rows.name:
We shall see to it that he is
punished to the fullest extent.

rows.label: qst201901_0420
rows.name:
Now, my beloved friends, let us go forth
to the imperial capital of Alba Margen!

rows.label: qst201901_0430
rows.name:
...Ah, the rest of you men and
beasts can be our luggage carriers.

rows.label: qst201901_0440
rows.name: Do not fall behind.

rows.label: qst201901_0450
rows.name: ...Hmph.
